sacd-vfs (0.1.83-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix early-EOF deadlock when DST audio ends before TOC frame count
  * Fill silence gaps (0x96 DSF pattern) instead of hanging on short tracks
  * Convert VFS_DEBUG from compile-time macro to runtime sa_log(DEBUG)
  * Add -v verbose flag (stackable: -v=verbose, -vv=debug, -vvv=trace)
  * Add -o log_level=LEVEL for explicit log level control
  * Enable timestamps and level prefixes in verbose/debug modes
  * Replace fprintf(stderr) warnings with sa_log(WARNING)
  * Add VERBOSE knob to systemd configuration
  * Remove mbedTLS dependency (no longer needed)
  * Add SACD_VFS_ONLY cmake option for standalone builds

 -- Alexander Wichers <sander.wichers@gmail.com>  Wed, 18 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000

sacd-vfs (0.1.81-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * FUSE3 virtual filesystem for SACD ISO images
  * Presents SACD discs as directories of DSF files
  * Systemd service with debconf configuration

 -- Alexander Wichers <sander.wichers@gmail.com>  Mon, 16 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000
